cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it proposes a new algorithm for distributed training of complex models on large-scale data. Other likely sub-categories include cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) as the paper deals with the challenges of handling non-IID data in distributed systems. Additionally, cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) are also possible sub-categories as the experiments were conducted on image datasets and the proposed algorithm involves optimization methods commonly used in neural networks.
